  • Classes in <Unnamed> used by <Unnamed> 
    Class Description
    APoint
    Mathematical method creating a point of coordinates x and y
    Enemy
    Creation of the aliens in this class, with their texture and conditions on their death
    GamePanel
    Main Panel calling every elements (SlingShot, Projectile, Aliens and Blocks) Display them and compute the launch of the projectile
    GameWindow
    Main Window containing all the games It contains GamePanel and the Game Loop
    Material
    Creation of the blocks in this class, with their texture and conditions on their destruction As well as future method for force computations
    Object
    Mother class of Materials, Aliens and Projectile Most of attributes are declared here and contains the code for the gravityAction and Collision Detection
    Projectile
    Method computing every characteristic of the projectile (Speed, Position, Display)
    Terrain
    Class containing the world where the game is played, filled with the background image and the elements aliens and blocks
    Thrower
    Class of the slingshot containing its computation methods and display
